Coaches have a huge impact in guiding athletes through these doubts and concerns, growing their confidence and helping them to excel in their sporting career. That’s why I was so delighted to bring my coach Aideen to speak about this with me to support the launch of Body Confident Sport, a first of its kind programme that helps coaches and mentors to instil body confidence and self-esteem in athletes aged 10-17.

Dove and Nike have teamed up to create resources to help coaches, teachers, mentors and parents to instill self-esteem and body confidence in young athletes. Such a brilliant initiative that can help young girls stay in sport for longer! 

If you are a coach, teacher, parent or guardian make sure to check out the video on YouTube and visit the link in my stories to find out more. 

#KeepHerConfident @Dove
